decks.notes: This deck is built around the companion card Lurrus of the Dream-Den, which allows the player to have an additional card in their starting hand. The deck focuses on aggressive strategies and aims to quickly overwhelm the opponent. It includes powerful artifacts like Mox Jet, Mox Sapphire, and Black Lotus to generate mana quickly. The deck also has disruptive elements like Force of Will and Lavinia, Azorius Renegade to disrupt the opponent's plans. Overall, the key concept of this deck is to use aggressive tactics, powerful artifacts, and disruptive elements to gain an advantage and defeat the opponent swiftly.
